<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-play-live-betting">How to Play Live Betting</h3>
<ol>
<li><p>Tap on &quot;Live Betting&quot; at the Home page.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Select a specific sport you would like to bet on. Sports include Football, Basketball, Tennis, Rugby, Cricket, Volleyball, Ice Hockey, Darts and Beach Volleyball.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Select a live match if you wish to check the real-time changes of such a match. Statistics and the match tracker are available for your reference.</p>
</li>
<li><p>The market list is displayed under a selected match.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Choose events you wish to play and select the odds by clicking on them. The chosen selections (no more than 30) will be automatically added to the betslip.</p>
</li>
<li><p>A message will be displayed to inform whether a bet has been successfully placed or not.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Tap on &quot;Schedule&quot; to check which matches will have live betting or to place a prematch bet for upcoming matches, including daily upcoming and next four days&#39; matches.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>